WEBVTT

00:00.258 --> 00:01.947
Previously on The Fosters...

00:01.986 --> 00:03.206
Hope you're pacing yourself, Mike.

00:03.222 --> 00:05.185
Dad, I'm gonna miss this
audition. Where are you?

00:05.209 --> 00:06.640
- You were late.
- I'm sorry.

00:06.679 --> 00:07.570
And you stink like booze.

00:07.617 --> 00:09.017
Or maybe I should just tell moms,

00:09.064 --> 00:10.143
who you've been talking to.

00:10.182 --> 00:12.262
I wish I could help, but
I don't have any more.

00:12.301 --> 00:14.155
I mean, there probably is
something at your house,

00:14.202 --> 00:16.587
something that your moms wouldn't
miss. And I could sell it.

00:16.642 --> 00:19.520
I should have realised that
you were never into Brandon.

00:19.559 --> 00:21.545
- He's into you.
- Oh, we're walking home

00:21.576 --> 00:22.484
Why don't you come with us?

00:22.515 --> 00:24.770
- Oh, no. I'm staying.
- Are you sure you're ok?

00:24.804 --> 00:27.539
- I'm great.
- You're not sending me to boarding school.

00:27.574 --> 00:30.542
- I don't know what they told you...
- I'm undocumented.

00:30.577 --> 00:34.413
And so are you. And if you send me
anywhere, I'll call immigration myself.

00:34.447 --> 00:37.583
Stay away from me, stay away
from Sarah, or else you're...

00:37.617 --> 00:39.351
Wyatt, let him go!

00:39.386 --> 00:41.420
I told you to stay out of it
and now you've made it worse.

00:41.454 --> 00:42.588
Fine, I'll stay out of it for good.

00:44.000 --> 00:50.074
